              <span>Research misconduct investigations and ORI coordination</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-600 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span>Clinical trial agreement negotiations and budget reviews</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </details>
      
